OL,5, Adidas has banned football fans from   
OL,6, buying German football kits customised 
OL,7, with the number 44, after media raised 
OL,8, its resemblance to the symbol used by  
OL,9, World War Two-era Nazi SS units.       
OL,11,F"We will block personalisation of the  
OL,12,Fjerseys," an Adidas spokesman said.    
OL,14,FSS units were the most responsible for 
OL,15,Fcrimes against humanity committed by   
OL,16,Fthe Nazis.                             
OL,18,FThe newly released kit has also caused 
OL,19,Fcontroversy with its choice of pink for
OL,20,Fthe away colours.                      
